== Amateka ==
Kevine Kagirimpundu n'umunyarwanda kazi wavukiye mu [[Rwanda]] I [[Kigali]] muri 1991 akurira mu muryango urimo abanyabugeni benshi bituma akurana inyota yo kuzakora ikintu gishya yihangiye mu bugenyi kizaza kije gutanga itandukaniro mubindi byari bisanzwe. Yarangije amashuri ye ya kaminuza muri [[Kaminuza nkuru yâ€™u Rwanda]] mu ishami rya creative design and environment muri 2015. Yagiye abona nizindi mpamya bushobozi mu bigendanye n'ubumenyi  bw'imiyoborere  n'iterambere ry'icyaro ndetse no guteza imbere abagore.<ref>https://bukzone.com/uzuri-ky-an-african-inspired-eco-footwear-persevering-the-environment-and-creating-jobs/</ref>

== Mu Bucuruzi ==
Kevine Kagirimpundu afatanije na mugenzi we Ysolde Shimwe  bashinze [[Uzuri K&Y]] mu mwaka wa 2013, bakaba baraje mu ruhando rwaba rwiyemezamirimo bateza imbere made in Rwanda ndetse bakaba barabiherewe igihembo na (RDB) [[Ikigo gishinzwe iterambere mu Rwanda]]<ref>https://twitter.com/rdbrwanda/status/1085920552366280704?lang=en</ref> sibyo gusa ahubwo bahawe n'ibihembo byinshi bitandukanye nibigo byinshi harimo best women startup Kora coaching group muri 2016, made in Rwanda expertise of the year bahawe na RDB muri 2018, top ten african heroes of the year bahawe na Jackma foundation yo mubushinywa muri 2019 ndetse na social entrepreneurship accelerator bahawe na Acumen & IKEA muri 2020<ref>https://about.uzuriky.com/</ref>

Uzuri K&Y izwiho gukora inkweto nziza zikomeye za made in Rwanda zifite umwihariko ndetse n'ubwiza. sibyo gusa ahubwo bagira n'udukapu ndetse n'udupira.

